<B>The Federalist Society Tenth Annual National Lawyers convention</B>
<P>
Washington, DC:  November 14-16

<P>
The Federalist Society will host their Tenth Annual National Lawyers
Convention at the Mayflower Hotel in downtown Washington. The
convention will begin with a series of fifteen breakout sessions
focusing on such things as environmental law and property rights,
religious freedom, and telecommunications. A plenary session of
the convention will gather for a national conference titled &quot;Prospects
for Constitutional Reform:  Congress, the Courts, and the Case
for Self-Discipline.&quot; The event will also feature a reception
and banquet. CONTACT: The Federalist Society, 1700 K Street, N.W.,
Suite 901, Washington, DC 20006, 202/822-8138, fax 202/296-8061.<hr>
<P>
