<P>
Richmond, VA: November 15-16

<P>
Campus leaders will gather in Richmond to explore free market
economics, current public policy issues, and the future of the
conservative movement.  The conference will include activist training
which will &quot;enable students to become more effective in advocating
their beliefs.&quot; CONTACT: Kristen Kingsley, 110 Elden Street,
Herndon, VA 20170, 800/292-9231, fax 703/318-9122.<hr>
