<P>
Washington, D.C.: December 3-8, 1996

<P>
The American Legislative Exchange Council will host its National
Orientation Conference for new members of state legislatures in
Washington, D.C., on December 3-8. The conference offers attendees
the information and insights needed for them to launch a successful
legislative career.  CONTACT: American Legislative Exchange Council,
910 17th Street, N.W., Fifth Floor, Washington, D.C. 20006, 202/466-3800,
fax 202/466-3801.<hr>
