with Non-Educational Functions; The Case for a Flat Tax on Property to Fund an Adequate Education in 
New Hampshires Public Schools; and Innovation in the State Personnel System: Telecommuting, Part-
time and Pooled Professionals. 52 pp. CONTACT: The Josiah Bartlett Center for Public Policy, P.O. Box 
