<P>
<I><font size=3>Just Doing It 2</FONT></I><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">,
published by the National Scholarship Center, is their second
annual survey of the private scholarship movement for precollege
education. With this year's survey they broaden their scope and
update their efforts from last year. From a single program launched
in Indianapolis in 1991, the precollege private scholarship movement
