<head>
<title>LI-Capitol Hill Staff Training School</title>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<img src="sc-logo.gif">
<p>


<h2>Capitol Hill Staff Training School</h2>
<center><b>Internet Applicants receive $25 discount on registration</b></center>
</center>
<pre><b>	
			1996

			Washington, DC  - November 14-15 
			Washington, DC  - December 12-13

			1997

			Washington, DC - January 30-31
			Washington, DC - April 3-4
			Washington, DC - June 26-27
			Washington, DC - November 10-13 (Evenings)
</b></pre><p>
The Capitol Hill Staff Training School is one of the best ways to land a job with a conservative member of Congress.  The faculty of Congressmen, senior level congressional staff members and legislative aides will teach you how to:<br>
<ul>
<li>Make your resume stand out from the rest
<li>Organize a congressional office
<li>Take a bill from concept to passage
<li>Network your way into a job on Capitol Hill
</ul>
At least one Congressman makes the Leadership Institute's Capitol Hill Staff Training School a pre-requisite for employment.  Other offices send top staff members who hire students straight from our classroom.
<p>
This school is a sure way to increase your skills for the Capitol Hill job market!
<p>
<center>
<b>For more information contact Brian Scully at (703) 321-8580 or fax (703) 247-2001</b><br>
</center>
