<html>
<head>
<title>LI-Candidate Development School</title>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<img src="sc-logo.gif">
<p>
<h2>Candidate Development School</h2>
<center><b>Internet Applicants receive $25 discount on registration</b></center>
</center>
<pre><b>
			1997

			Washington, DC - July 23-27
</b></pre><p>
<b>Prepare today for a winning candidacy.</b>
<p>
Not how to run for office, but how to prepare yourself to be a good candidate later on.
<p>
The five day <b>Candidate Development School</b> introduces you to key experts on hot public policy issues.  It prepares prospective candidates for future careers in elected public office. 
<p>
Half the school is about issues, the other half teaches you how to build a strong political base and fundraising base.
<p>
Learn from the best.<P>  The faculty of more than 40 experts includes conservative Congressmen, prominent conservative leaders, nationally known activists and others in the public policy process -- a ready-made network of powerful new friends.
<p>
<center>
<b>For more information contact David Gersten 1-800-827-LEAD or fax (703) 247-2001<br></b>
</center>
<p>
<a href="rg-sc-cd.html"><img src="reg2.gif" ALT="Register" BORDER=0></a><a href="sc-com.html#cd"><img src="scom.gif" ALT="Student Comments" BORDER=0></a><a href="sc-cd-ag.html"><img src="agenda.gif" ALT="School Agenda" BORDER=0></a><a href="home.html"><img src="home.gif" ALT="Home" BORDER=0></a></b><a href="mailto:lead@townhall.com"><img src="email2.gif" ALT="E-mail" BORDER=0></a>
